Value: Metal Bank Limited engages in the exploration and development of mineral properties. Its primary projects include the 8 Mile, Eidsvold, and Wild Irishman projects situated in the northern New England Fold Belt of central Queensland. The company has an option to hold 80% interest in the Millennium, a copper-cobalt-gold exploration and development project located in the Mount Isa region of northwest Queensland. Metal Bank Limited was incorporated in 2007 and is based in Sydney, Australia.
